Emily Stevens (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emily_Stevens_(actress) 0 Emily Stevens (February 27, 1883 – January 2, 1928) was a stage and screen actress in Broadway plays in the first three decades of the 20th century and later in silent movies.
